message: The multi-jurisdictional task force is designed as a collaborative network to identify those at risk, raise awareness, provide training and address gaps in services for individuals who are trafficked.

data.description: Representatives from more than 20 local agencies plan to sign a Memorandum of Understanding on Thursday, September 14 to officially outline the Rock County Anti-Human Trafficking Task Force’s…
data.title: Anti-human trafficking task force signs memorandum of understanding
